  - dialogueText: 'Oh... nothing, it''s just... um... I was thinking about my family,
      who live in the West, and sometimes when I do that my old accent comes back.

      I
      shouldn''t be so self-conscious about it, but people can get very sensitive
      when it comes to those things.'
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828017962
